{"tid":2383558,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"此古戰場也。嘗覆三軍，往往鬼哭，天陰則聞","createTime":"2021-01-28T03:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T03:59:48.000Z","uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c52a739753a5eb1285c0686517b1d4988829e7a9","tid":2383558,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"屍填巨港之岸，血滿長城之窟。無貴無賤，同為枯骨，可勝言哉！鼓衰兮力竭，矢盡兮絃絕。白刃交兮寶刀折，兩軍蹙兮生死決。降矣哉，終身夷狄！戰矣哉，骨暴沙礫！鳥無聲兮山寂寂，夜正長兮風淅淅。魂魄結兮天沈沈，鬼神聚兮雲冪冪。日光寒兮草短，月色苦兮霜白。傷心慘目，有如是耶！"},{"pid":"3b068d92ccc00ce95150d4f09a24f3edec60cf74","tid":2383558,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a60817f419f2922b5fb2cf57684d568e8071c4","tid":2383558,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}